name: FingerPunk #008 (Lit Larry)
description: There's no need to tell Larry he's on fire, he already knows. The thing he hasn't figured out yet is how to put it out. He runs around the metaverse yelling and screaming, but he never stops for long enough to receive any help. Numerous other FingerPunks have tried to extinguish the conflagration, sadly they haven't yet succeeded.
